<subSubSection id="49C942EEFFEC3934EBD2C26BFD5B5ED8" pageId="66" pageNumber="67" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="016C1165FFEC3934EBD2C26BFEAA5E44" blockId="66.[227,341,1368,1394]" box="[227,341,1368,1394]" pageId="66" pageNumber="67">
<heading id="5A24A609FFEC3934EBD2C26BFEAA5E44" bold="true" box="[227,341,1368,1394]" fontSize="11" level="3" pageId="66" pageNumber="67" reason="3">
<emphasis id="33A7CD77FFEC3934EBD2C26BFEAA5E44" bold="true" box="[227,341,1368,1394]" pageId="66" pageNumber="67">Remarks</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="016C1165FFEC3934EBD2C2BAFD5B5ED8" blockId="66.[226,1436,1417,1519]" pageId="66" pageNumber="67">
The otoliths of this species seem most similar to those of Recent 
<taxonomicName id="C6D36AE6FFEC3934E8E8C2BAFB855E95" authorityName="Gunther" authorityYear="1862" box="[985,1146,1417,1443]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Citharidae" genus="Brachypleura" kingdom="Animalia" order="Pleuronectiformes" pageId="66" pageNumber="67" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="33A7CD77FFEC3934E8E8C2BAFB855E95" box="[985,1146,1417,1443]" italics="true" pageId="66" pageNumber="67">Brachypleura</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(see 
<bibRefCitation id="65426C94FFEC3934EF89C2BAFEFD5EFF" author="Schwarzhans" firstAuthor="Schwarzhans" page="87" pageId="66" pageNumber="67" pagination="1 - 391" refId="ref56763" refString="Schwarzhans W. 1999. A comparative morphological treatise of recent and fossil otoliths of the order Pleuronectiformes. In: Pfeil F. (ed.) Piscium Catalogus, Otolithi Piscium: 1 - 391. Verlag Dr. Freidrich Pfeil, Munich." type="book chapter" year="1999">Schwarzhans 1999: 87</bibRefCitation>
, figs 105–110 for otoliths of the Recent 
<taxonomicName id="C6D36AE6FFEC3934E9C6C29CFB655EFF" authority="Gunther, 1862" authorityName="Gunther" authorityYear="1862" box="[759,1178,1454,1481]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Citharidae" genus="Brachypleura" kingdom="Animalia" order="Pleuronectiformes" pageId="66" pageNumber="67" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="novaezeelandiae">
<emphasis id="33A7CD77FFEC3934E9C6C29CFC215EFE" box="[759,990,1454,1480]" italics="true" pageId="66" pageNumber="67">B. novaezeelandiae</emphasis>
Günther, 1862
</taxonomicName>
), and therefore, were assigned to that genus by 
<bibRefCitation id="65426C94FFEC3934E920C2E7FD5F5ED8" author="Nolf" box="[529,672,1492,1518]" firstAuthor="Nolf" pageId="66" pageNumber="67" refId="ref55849" refString="Nolf D. 2013. The Diversity of Fish Otoliths, Past and Present. Royal Belgian Institute of Natural Sciences, Brussels." type="book" year="2013">Nolf (2013)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
